trans-unit.source: This collection stores only whole dates.
trans-unit.target: Den här samlingen lagras endast hela datum.

trans-unit.source: The time portion of each <xref:System.DateTime?displayProperty=fullName> is removed.
trans-unit.target: Tidsdelen av varje <xref:System.DateTime?displayProperty=fullName>tas bort.</xref:System.DateTime?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.target: Datumen lagras i stigande ordning.

trans-unit.source: If there are duplicate dates, only one date is stored in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Om det finns dubbla datum, lagras endast ett datum i samlingen.
